Comment: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.06,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Let me say here from the start that...
Comment: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.38,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Let me say here from the start that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:21.68,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,...esta historia es la misma para mí.{... this tale is the same for me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:27.10,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Una historia para informarte que, contrario a la idea que Araragi-kun hace de mí, como alguna clase de santa histórica o una madre santa, {A tale to let you know that contrary to Araragi’s portrayals \Nof me as some kind of historical saint or holy mother,}
