Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.82,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Para informarte que soy una gata,{To let you know that I am a cat,}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.48,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,y que soy un tigre.{and that I am a tiger.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.50,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Y...{And...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.16,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,...que soy una persona.{... that I am a person.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.54,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Una historia de traiciones...{A tale of betrayal...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.42,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,...hecha para decepcionar a todos.{... made to let everyone down.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.88,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,No creo que sea capaz de contarla bien, de la manera que lo hace Araragi-kun,{I don’t think I’ll be able to \Ntell it well, the way Araragi can,}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:51.88,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,pero me gustaría intentarlo de oído y dar lo mejor que pueda.{but I’d like to play it by ear and try my best.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:57.30,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Imagino que esa es la forma que cualquiera hablaría sobre su propia vida.{I imagine that’s the way anyone would talk \Nabout his or her own life.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.88,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Ahora.{Now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.98,Hanekawa,,0,0,0,,Ha llegado el momento de despertar de esta pesadilla.{The time has come to wake from this nightmare.}
